subSubSection.paragraph:
Hortophora transmarina

comb. nov. has been found along the east coast of Australia from southern New South Wales to the Top End, but also into the northern parts of the Northern Territory and Western Australia (Fig. 
26
). The species has also been found in Papua New Guinea (
Chrysanthus 1960
).
